OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNo VAT cut to household    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fenergy bills in the Budget 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, VAT on household energy bills will not 
OL,6, be cut in the Chancellor's Budget on   
OL,7, Wednesday, despite calls to help       
OL,8, families struggling with soaring       
OL,9, prices.                                
OL,11,FLabour has been calling for the rate to
OL,12,Fbe slashed from 5% to zero for the next
OL,13,Fsix months to help households get      
OL,14,Fthrough a "tough winter".              
OL,16,FBut Whitehall sources have told the BBC
OL,17,Fsuch a move would be poorly targeted.  
OL,19,FThey say lower income households can be
OL,20,Fbetter helped through other schemes.   
